        <abstract>
            <p>The Copley Medal is considered a great honour, but such things make little difference to CD, except for the several kind letters he received. It shows that natural selection is making some progress.</p>
            <p>His health is poor.</p> 
<p>Work is crawling on <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>;</p> 
            <p>occasional botany recreative.</p>
        </abstract>
